commit.message:
builtins.def (inf, inff, infl): Mark const.

        * builtins.def (inf, inff, infl): Mark const.
        (huge_val, huge_valf, huge_vall): Likewise.
        (BUILT_IN_GETEXP, BUILT_IN_GETMAN): Remove.

From-SVN: r56926

 	* real.c (ereal_inf): Clear E before use.
